{"results"=>[{"id"=>"bkn__73511", "name"=>"Phoenicia Hotel Beirut", "coordinates"=>{"latitude"=>33.90056995, "longitude"=>35.494894849999994}, "score"=>9.089242242595, "intro"=>"The Phoenicia Hotel Beirut is a historic 5-star luxury hotel situated in the Minet El Hosn neighborhood of Beirut, Lebanon. It is located on Rue Fakhreddine near the Corniche Beirut promenade and walking-distance from Beirut Central District, and a few kilometers from Beirut Rafic Hariri International Airport. The Phoenicia is part of the worldwide InterContinental Hotels chain, but it dropped the actual use of the chain name in 2012.", "properties"=>[{"key"=>"phone", "name"=>"Phone", "value"=>"+961 1 369 100", "ordinal"=>2}, {"key"=>"email", "name"=>"Email", "value"=>"phoenicia@phoenicia-ic.com", "ordinal"=>3}, {"key"=>"address", "name"=>"Address", "value"=>"Ain El Mraisseh/Minet El Hosn", "ordinal"=>4}, {"key"=>"fax", "name"=>"Fax", "value"=>"+961 1-369101", "ordinal"=>5}, {"key"=>"website", "name"=>"Website", "value"=>"http://phoeniciabeirut.com/", "ordinal"=>6}], "snippet"=>"Overlooking the Mediterranean Sea, the InterContinental Phoenicia Beirut is situated along the famous boardwalk, “Corniche” a few minutes from the city’s business and banking district, and the ever lively and entertaining city center.", "location_id"=>"Beirut", "hotels_score"=>9.089242242595}, {"id"=>"bkn__74432", "name"=>"Crowne Plaza Beirut Hotel", "coordinates"=>{"latitude"=>33.89555556, "longitude"=>35.47916667}, "score"=>8.37362574428083, "intro"=>"The Crowne Plaza Beirut Hotel is a five-star Crowne Plaza hotel in Beirut, Lebanon. Inaugurated on 22 September 2001, it is the first Crowne Plaza to open in Lebanon. The modern tower makes a notable mark on the landscape, overlooking Hamra Street in the downtown Hamra district. Fady Sawaya, a hotelier with previous experience in Intercontinental Phoenicia, Beirut, and InterContinental Hotel Abu Dhabi was appointed manager early in 2012.", "properties"=>[], "snippet"=