lding built in the late 1920s.", "location_id"=>"Beirut", "hotels_score"=>7.56604443765196}, {"id"=>"T__3e4a1276e5c6", "name"=>"Hilton Beirut Metropolitan Palace", "coordinates"=>{"latitude"=>33.87076749825985, "longitude"=>35.53604803890675}, "score"=>7.45347673201551, "intro"=>"The Hilton Beirut Metropolitan Palace is a five-star hotel in Beirut, Lebanon. Located in the Sin el Fil district, the hotel has 195 rooms, 11 executive suites, 5 diplomatic suites, a presidential suite, a royal suite, an imperial suite and a penthouse suite.\nThe hotel contains a range of restaurants, notably Italian cuisine in the Venezia Restaurant and Oriental cuisine in the Summer Place. The Al Shindagah serves a range of international cuisine.", "properties"=>[{"key"=>"phone", "name"=>"Phone", "value"=>"+961 1 496 666", "ordinal"=>2}, {"key"=>"email", "name"=>"Email", "value"=>"BeirutMetropolitanpalace.Information@hilton.com", "ordinal"=>3}, {"key"=>"address", "name"=>"Address", "value"=>"Dimitri El Hayek", "ordinal"=>4}, {"key"=>"fax", "name"=>"Fax", "value"=>"+961-1-502502", "ordinal"=>5}, {"key"=>"website", "name"=>"Website", "value"=>"https://www3.hilton.com/en/hotels/lebanon/hilton-beirut-metropolitan-palace-BEYMPHI/index.html?WT.mc_id=zELWAKN0EMEA1HI2DMH3LocalSearch4DGGenericx6BEYMPHI", "ordinal"=>6}], "snippet"=>"The hotel contains a range of restaurants, notably Italian cuisine in the Venezia Restaurant and Oriental cuisine in the Summer Place.", "location_id"=>"Beirut", "hotels_score"=>7.45347673201551}, {"id"=>"T__f87001c7b46e", "name"=>"Radisson Blu Martinez Hotel", "coordinates"=>{"latitude"=>33.9001193355738, "longitude"=>35.49258476360603}, "score"=>7.35151734509635, "intro"=>"Radisson Blu Martinez Hotel is a hotel in Beirut.", "properties"=>[{"key"=>"phone", "name"=>"Phone", "value"=>"+961 1 368 111", "ordinal"=>1}, {"key"=>"email", "name"=>"Email", "value"=>"reservations.beirut@radissonblu.com", "ordinal"=>2}, {"key"=>"address", "name"=>"Address", "value"=>"Ain El Mrey